{"tid":826460,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都三日兩夜行程分配","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T03:47:12.000Z","uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d639218e5627c51260763f636cad2ea5597560c7","tid":826460,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"小弟下個月會去日本玩一個星期, 會帶埋女朋友去大阪玩<br />\n暫時plan左係京都玩3日兩夜, 大阪玩4日3夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有個問題係落機時間係日本當地下就1點, 係關西機場去到京都check in完應該都3點鐘, 唔係好知可以去邊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫定行程:<br />\nDay 1 大阪機場-&gt; 京都酒店放抵行李(近京都站) -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">呢段時間可以點安排?</span><br />\n衝去伏見稻荷大社?, 夜晚會去京都站拉麵小路+行下京都站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 2  銀閣寺 - 哲學之道 - 南禪寺 - 清水寺-去租和服&gt; - 高台寺 - 祇園花見小路 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 嵐山 - 嵯峨小火車 - 渡月橋 - 天龍寺, 竹林小徑 - 野宮神社 &gt; 四條河源町+錦市場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 , 5 ,6 <br />\n一日會去USJ玩全日<br />\n一日去神戶動物王國+黑門市場行下<br />\n兩日就去下周遊卡既免費景點(摩天輪,天守閣)+奈良撚鹿+周圍shopping食野<br />\n仲考慮緊會唔會去海遊館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下大家會唔會有意見比我改善下個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368f2551fc14f751ef71048a7e886385e651abaa","tid":826460,"uid":181905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"check in完當然即刻扑野先<br />\n<br />\n海遊館就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1b9c498d21ce11eb340e089bccf82d16963dc0","tid":826460,"uid":31629,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"1點落機你想3點就checkin完你班機喺京都降落?<br />\ncheckin完起碼都5點啦"},{"pid":"d2ce25eb33bef925dfe2259baa4b5fdf3b6f8e8f","tid":826460,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"368f2551fc14f751ef71048a7e886385e651abaa","tid":826460,"uid":181905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"check in完當然即刻扑野先<br />\n<br />\n海遊館就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都係扑一個鐘, 仲有好多時間淨<br />\n海遊館有d人又話值得去, 有d人有話不值一提<br />\n好難捉摸丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6b56c131e88d5918d096ee7a34b4ebc5da4257","tid":826460,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1b9c498d21ce11eb340e089bccf82d16963dc0","tid":826460,"uid":31629,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"1點落機你想3點就checkin完你班機喺京都降落?<br />\ncheckin完起碼都5點啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟第一次去大阪京都, 唔係好熟路程, 原諒我啦<br />\n咁5點打後仲夠唔夠時間去一個景點玩?"},{"pid":"554b8df61b00c5a30be520610f021d004db9476e","tid":826460,"uid":181905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2ce25eb33bef925dfe2259baa4b5fdf3b6f8e8f","tid":826460,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"368f2551fc14f751ef71048a7e886385e651abaa","tid":826460,"uid":181905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"check in完當然即刻扑野先<br />\n<br />\n海遊館就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都係扑一個鐘, 仲有好多時間淨<br />\n海遊館有d人又話值得去, 有d人有話不值一提<br />\n好難捉摸丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"去行yodobashi囉 行成日都未行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecef82116fbea87414614142efb66eb607da7d9","tid":826460,"uid":31629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,